    {
      "id": "1b44750c-f3ba-8000-8438-eaeeca143f71",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The objective of the work is to recommend online resources so that students can develop their course Learning Outcomes. The authors create their own dataset and use it to create a student to CLO matrix using a bi-clustering approach.",
